---
title: Goulash-Style Pasta with Beyond Meat® and Roasted Peppers
description: We've created a HelloFresh twist on a classic goulash with herby, smoky Beyond Meat. Hungarian goulash is neither a soup nor a stew, but something in between; we hope you enjoy this 'stoup'!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beyond-meat-goulash-style-pasta-870733e6.jpg
